text
@d1 1
a1 1
.\" $OpenBSD: zts.4,v 1.1 2005/04/17 12:41:59 dlg Exp $
d34 2
a35 5
Touching and removing the stylus from the screen will generate mouse down and
up events on
.Xr wsmouse 4
button 0.
Events may be generated by holding the
d37 1
a37 1
(button 1) or
d39 2
a40 1
(button 2) keys down while tapping.
